product_name: MaybellineSuper Lock Brow Glue Waterproof Eyebrow Gel
summary: SummarySculpt & set brows for 24hrs with Maybelline Super Lock Waterproof Brow Glue. Tinted, non-sticky, flake-resistant & waterproof.
details: DetailsBenefitsSculpted & styled brows locked in with up to 24-hour super holdLong-lasting, flake-resistant, sweat-resistant & transfer-resistantDelivers a non-sticky, comfortable finishComes with its own brow styling brush that quickly sculpts & styles hairs into a desired shape that lastsItem 2624895How To UseLightly brush hairs in upward and outward strokes.Never apply this product in a moving vehicle.IngredientsAqua/Water/Eau, Beheneth-30, VP/VA Copolymer, Alcohol, Pentylene Glycol, Butylene Glycol, Glycerin, Dipropylene Glycol, Phenoxyethanol, Caprylyl Glycol, Xanthan Gum.
how_to_use: Lightly brush hairs in upward and outward strokes.Never apply this product in a moving vehicle.

reviews.headline: Great formula!
reviews.comments: This is not too think or thin. It keeps my brows in place. It feels solid but not rock hard once it's dried. I do wipe off some product before putting a thin layer on my brows.

reviews.headline: I WOULD BUY THIS PRODUCT AGAIN AND AGAIN
reviews.comments: this brow gel is the best!!! I def recommend this to anyone looking for a low priced brow gel. It feels very high end. It sticks nicely without the icky feeling on the brows. This gel lasts all day! Very nice finish to the brows and the packaging is convenient. The little spoolie isn't getting the product anywhere but the brows which is great!

reviews.headline: Great product
reviews.comments: Works great this really holds your eyebrows in place without any flaking!

reviews.headline: Smudge proofe
reviews.comments: Definitely have never used anything like this before. Glues my eyebrows still and lasts, I had this on when it rained and it kept my eyebrows still and kept the color on without any accidents and smudges

reviews.headline: Only brow makeup I need
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I already loved their eyebrow gel that was clear, but this having tint takes it to a whole new level. Love the subtle darkness it provides while also keeping the brow in place. Great applicator and amazing value.

reviews.headline: Brows aren't movin'
reviews.comments: Here is the deal: your brows need to be clean for this producy to work properly. That said, my brow hairs will stay in place for 10+ hours.

reviews.headline: Adding the Super lock tinted brow glue to my make up routine
reviews.comments: I was sent the Super tinted brow glue for my honest review. I truly enjoy this product. A simple tinted glue on the brows and ready to go! This is going to be added to my make up routine!

reviews.headline: Wasn't the best for me
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] Maybelline Super Lock Tinted Brow Glue wasn't a win for me. Since my brows are already thick and full, the product didn't give me the hold I was looking for. My brows never stayed in place, and the tint didn't really add much definition. It might work better for someone with finer brows, but for me, it didn't deliver the strong hold it claims.

reviews.headline: Nice!
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] Im not one who usually does anything with my eyebrows but this was pretty easy to use. I think you get plenty of product for the packaging. Definitely worth the money!

reviews.headline: Amazing
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This brow gel is amazing!! I use it almost every day. It has a nice brush applicator and it completely freezes your brows exactly how you brush them. It last more than 24 hours for sure. It also doesn't look unnatural. My only issue is that if I'm not careful removing it, I can accidentally rip out some eyebrow hairs by scrubbing too hard.

reviews.headline: Works but can get messy
reviews.comments: When I first opened this product, it was good but a bit messy. After about two weeks of using it, I noticed that the brush started to become clumpy and my eyebrows would have white "flakes" left on them from the dried gel. I thought this would ruin it for me, but my solution was cleaning off the brush and the top of the packaging, and my issues were solved. I actually now love this more than ever, and would repurchase it. My eyebrows are held in place theoughout the entire day and it doesn't feel uncomforable.

reviews.headline: I love this product :)
reviews.comments: I used to buy the NYX brow glue but i felt like it never dried down with a strong hold. It dried down more sticky and the applicator was not my fav. HOWEVERRR this Maybeline Superlock brow glue has won me over. The hold is phenomenal and my brows dont go anywhere, the applicator is really nice as well i love how it coats all of my hairs evenly. My brows dont feel heavy from the gel either, this is genuinely a good brow gel for such a good price too and it will last you many uses.

reviews.headline: Daily use
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] Good for everyday, I like that it doesn't turn white which a lot of brow gels tend too. I apply let it dry for 2/3 mins before finishing the rest of my makeup and I'm out the door looking out together. Just place it in your bag and go, you can't beat it

reviews.headline: Hate.
reviews.comments: White pilling textured residue (like glue messaged into skin) up and down the brow. not cute. will return as soon as I find the energy.

reviews.headline: Buy it immediately
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I really liked this brow product it was the perfect shade for me. My brows are pretty thin and this helped make the stand out in a good way!

reviews.headline: Decent
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] This is a pretty good eyebrow product intuitive and using and easy to apply. Not too expensive for how well it stays I would buy again. Not sure how long lasting the product is.

[I received this product in exchange for my honest review] 10/10! I have used so many brow gels/pencils! This is by far my fav and the most affordable!!! Stays all day, doesn't dry weird. Looks and feels great!

reviews.headline: 10/10 brows
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] 10/10! I have used so many brow gels/pencils! This is by far my fav and the most affordable!!! Stays all day, doesn't dry weird. Looks and feels great!

reviews.headline: Love and easy to use
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I've used lots of brow gel tinted and clear and this did a great job holding my brows in place all day. For the price I wouldn't look any further as this held up great!

reviews.headline: Tinted brow gel
reviews.comments: [I received this product in exchange for my honest review] I love this tinted brow gel. It's easy to apply, look very natural and the packaging is small enough to fit in any purse. Definitely a great price point. It shapes and keeps my brows in place. It has no unpleasant smell. I would rate a 10/10.

faceoff_positive.comments:
[I received this product in exchange for my honest review] My New Holy Grail that Out Perform...
I've always struggled to find a good eyebrow gel to keep my brows in place. I've tried almost every high-end brand out there, and they always seem to be lacking in some way. My thoughts when I first tried the Maybelline Super Lock Brow Glue was,
"Wow!" How have I been searching so hard all this
time when the answer was on the shelf at my local drugstore the entire time! First off, the no fuss packaging is simple with a squeezable tube and a handy little brush that works really well for applying and shaping my eyebrows. It applies clear and dries within about a minute, which gives me plenty of time to shape them. The gel does not affect my brow powder or brow pencil the way some formulas do, so no more mess trying to fix the color after applying my brow gel. The formula is not sticky at all and is a perfect consistency. The real surprise here was the effectiveness. This truly is like a glue. Your brows will not move an inch for the entire day! This was still on after a day of hiking in rainy weather. You can't ask for much more. It also easily came off at night with my regular makeup removing routine. This product out performs every single high-end formula I have tried to date. I'm beyond happy that I found this.
This will be my holy grail eyebrow gel from now on!
faceoff_positive.headline: I would buy this again

faceoff_negative.comments:
I've been testing out the Maybelline Super Stay Brow Glue and while there's a lot to like about it, there's one quirk that's worth mentioning. The holding power? Absolutely there â€“ it does a solid job at keeping my brows in place all day, which is exactly what you'd expect from a product with 'glue' in its name.

However, I've noticed that after it dries, it can leave a bit of a milky residue behind, casting a slightly white shadow in my brows. This isn't ideal, especially since the rest of the product works so well. If you're someone who needs a heavy-duty brow setter and don't mind doing a bit of touch-up, this might not be a deal-breaker.

Despite this little hiccup, the Maybelline Super Stay Brow Glue is a good product and has all the makings of a go-to for tamed brows. Just be aware of that potential for a milky cast, and maybe keep a spoolie brush handy to buff out any white residue that might show up after drying.
faceoff_negative.headline: Good but better for lighter brows
